    "description": "IACE TRAVEL Corporation., together with its subsidiaries, engages in the travel business in Japan, Canada, and Mexico. The company offers business travel management (BTM) services, such as air ticket and accommodation arrangements for domestic and international business trips, immigration information, visa applications, payment settlement, risk management, and business trip data. It also operates Smart BTM, a cloud-based travel booking system with online reservation functionality that provides data analysis and proposals for cost reduction, multiple route suggestions, urgent booking arrangements, and a 24/7 emergency response system. In addition, the company provides personal travel services comprising domestic and international package tours, personal travel arrangements, custom travel proposals, and other benefits-related services; travel agency support services for government bodies, such as personal trips and home visits; airline ticketing, travel planning, and guided tours for U.S. military personnel based in Japan; flight bookings to Japan and international tours departing from Canada; and incentive travel and personal travel support for employees of Japanese corporations in Mexico. It serves corporate clients, individual travelers, government agencies, and the U.S. military in Japan. IACE TRAVEL Corporation. was founded in 1975 and is headquartered in Chuo, Japan."
